$! File name  :  COMPILE_XTI.COM
$! Purpose    :  Compile source code for XTI_LIB.OLB program
$!
$! Version :	 14-JAN-94
$!
$ ON ERROR THEN GOTO EXIT
$!
$! Compile everything
